## Home services across Bandipora

Panun Kaergar connects **Bandipora** households with verified partners for everyday home repairs and improvements — in town and across **Sumbal**, **Hajin**, **Aloosa**, **Quil**, and **Ajas**.

Tell us your locality when you book. We check partner availability in your zone and confirm the visit time by phone, WhatsApp, website, or the app.
